data.description: Beautifully Remodeled 3 Bedroom 1 1/2 Bath Brick Home.  Quality Impeccable Spotless move-in ready home. Spacious Brand New Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances with Manufacture Warranty. Upgraded Soft-Close Hardwood Cabinets with Large Breakfast Island with lots of Cabinet storage underneath. Four Drawer Stack Cabinets. New 12x24 Tile Flooring.  Dinning or Breakfast area with French doors with view of the backyard. New Updated Completely Remodeled Bathrooms. Bedrooms with New Ceiling Fans, Doors, Blinds and Carpet. Brand New Trane A/C Unit with Warranty.  Landscaped front yard with New Concrete Driveway. Backyard with New Concrete Patio Slab perfect for grilling. Storage room off the side of the house near back door. 1 Car Carport with covered walkway to side door. Fenced backyard. New Architectural Shingle Roof with newly updated plywood sheathing. This Home is located in great location in a quiet established Neighborhood.  More pictures to come. Call or Text 904-778-6865
